---
title: Mimi’s Nutty Tom Yum Noodle Broth with Pickled Radishes
description: This noodle broth is absolutely packed with different flavours and textures. Noodles, crushed peanuts and you even get to learn about pickling radishes! And you know what else is so great about this recipe? It’s seasonal and radishes are our British Veggie of the Month.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mimis-nutty-tom-yum-noodle-broth-21-8b4567.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/mimis-nutty-tom-yum-noodle-broth-8b4567.pdf
servings: 2
